content.rendered:
SO LIGHT AND AMAZING!!

So my favorite snack almost ever is tomatoes and mozzarella. And for the past three months I have cut out cheese, and so this is my new love!

What you will need:

1 medium sized tomato

1/2 avocado

Olive Oil

Handful of diced onions

Pepper

Salt

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

Slice tomatoes and put them on a plate.

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

Mash up the avocado and place a dollop on each tomato slice.

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

Drizzle on olive oil, salt and pepper.

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

 

Top with some onions!

 

YUMMYYYYY!!!!

 

Great snack or appetizer!!
